    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Compilers of bibliographies, which are lists of books, periodical articles, and audiovisual materials on specialized subjects, annotate bibliographies with physical descriptors, and analyze subject content of materials. Also, scholars of books as physical objects and those who advise on the acquisition of materials in special subjects. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000012251/U.S. Employment Service, Dictionary of Occupational Titles (1977)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000050615/IFLA Glossary for Art Librarians (1984)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Personas que compilan listas de libros, artículos períodicos, y material audiovisual en temas especializados, comentan bibliografías con descriptores físicos y analizan contenidos temáticos de materiales; también aquellos que aconsejan en la adquisición de material en temas específicos.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Personen die lijsten van boeken, tijdschriftartikelen en audiovisueel materiaal over gespecialiseerde onderwerpen samenstellen, bibliografiën met fysieke descriptoren annoteren en het onderwerp van het materiaal analyseren. Ook zij die adviseren over de verwerving van materiaal over speciale onderwerpen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>書誌編纂者；書誌內容依據特定主題羅列書籍、期刊文章以及特定主題之視聽教材。書誌學家負責為書誌提供內容註解並分析題材宗旨。此詞彙亦指研究實體學術書籍以及針對如何蒐集特定題材資料提供建議的學者。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
